readme:
# vega-voronoi

Voronoi diagram transform for Vega dataflows.

This module provides the following Vega data transform:

- [**Voronoi**](https://vega.github.io/vega/docs/transforms/voronoi/) [<>](https://github.com/vega/vega-voronoi/blob/master/src/Voronoi.js "Source")
